{"about_the_game":"Exophobia is a retro inspired sci-fi FPS with modern metroidvania progression, mixing crisp colorful pixel art with intense electronic music for a unique stylish aesthetic!<br><br>You find yourself alone in a human spaceship taken over by hostile alien soldiers. Explore and fight your way to find the last human survivors, while you uncover piece by piece the backstory of the spaceship crew, leading to this high-stakes moment at the red planet. <strong>Evolve your alien weapon and shoot, slide, stun your enemies and more, in your journey to escape out alive!</strong><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189220/extras/KillReduced.gif?t=1734906074\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">KILL</h2>Experience FPS gameplay where quick reflexes and clever positioning are vital to survive. Learn each enemy behavior and use your weapon,  movement options and surroundings to eliminate diverse groups of alien armies in fast paced action filled combat. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189220/extras/ExploreReduced.gif?t=1734906074\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EXPLORE</h2>Discover a spaceship with multiple floors, each featuring a unique hostile environment. From worm infested laboratories to the mechanical inner workings of the spaceship engine, with plenty of secrets for the curious explorers!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189220/extras/UpgradeReduced.gif?t=1734906074\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">UPGRADE</h2>Improve your weapon with a new ability every time you reach a specialized weapon laboratory. In metroidvania fashion, these abilities drastically empower you in combat and also unlock previously inaccessible areas required to progress.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189220/extras/DieReduced.gif?t=1734906074\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DIE</h2>Challenge yourself with unforgiving but fair difficulty in diverse battle situations with ruthless enemies possessing unique attack patterns, including menacing boss fights, each with their own defeating strategy. Don't forget to save your progress in checkpoints!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Mecha No More","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1189220/f686e3e91ae80097e0b0f736a7355d82a623fd3b.jpg"},{"name":"Turning it on and off","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1189220/b79598e29e1028b97306fe4d62052e31e355f496.jpg"},{"name":"Secret Rival","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1189220/7a97bec8eed86c033e7363a45dab6f5598a8c8b2.jpg"},{"name":"Round 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1189220/de62095cef786699c7ed5c991ff1a7c2014be907.jpg"},{"name":"Final Clash","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1189220/38ca46745f5b6d2a152cadf8170a22ff36a2619f.jpg"},{"name":"GROSS!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1189220/41223a102c4005886c97fca79ecc657c9c3095d1.jpg"},{"name":"Born Ready","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1189220/f9c09bee9f815f1a794f5718f524f25d31a3a4fb.jpg"},{"name":"Charge","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1189220/44d17e0e3ced9f4556c525062f871c7c111c6e89.jpg"},{"name":"Shockwave","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1189220/326150a0a5f801c5c51124ea21466b74908a9673.jpg"},{"name":"Teleport","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1189220/ae336cb04f7331ea6fdad294bcf7efeaa50daf24.jpg"}],"total":45},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189220/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg